profile:
Reliable Repair Service

We provide professional and affordable repair services to clients in the Durham and Clarington area. When you have an issue with your electric or gas appliance, you need a trustworthy and professional technician to get the job done right. We respond to calls quickly and efficiently. Owner operated by a local licensed and insured technician. We pride ourselves on providing reasonable prices, while still using high quality parts. Providing service to all major brands, including but not limited to Whirlpool, Kenmore, Samsung, Frigidaire, Maytag, Kitchenaid, Amana, LG, GE, Electrolux and more. Unfortunately, sometimes appliances just can't be fixed, but we still have your back. Providing full installations for all new appliances.
